init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He sees people praying for his safe return.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He then sees a screen of his wife and children.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He sees them watching it all the time, even when they are eating.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt Damon then realizes that these aliens are not so different from us.
